quests.title: Level 10 Character (FINAL FANTASY XIII)
quests.description:
Raise a character from FINAL FANTASY XIII to level 10!
Snow is a character from the FINAL FANTASY XIII realm who can be recruited by completing The Hanging Edge (XIII) dungeon .
When fighting in dungeons from their native realm, characters get a Record Synergy bonus.
The Record Synergy bonus boosts characters' stats and the EXP they earn.
Recruit characters from each realm to have the perfect party ready at a moment's notice!
quests.achieve_cond_description: Raise any character from the FINAL FANTASY XIII realm to level 10 or higher.
